  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[On Play] Reveal the top 4 cards of your deck. Add 1 Digimon
    card with [Rock Dragon], [Earth Dragon], [Bird Dragon], [Machine Dragon], or
    [Sky Dragon] in its traits and 1 [Hina Kurihara] among them to your hand. Place
    the rest at the bottom of your deck in any order.'
